examples.en: He returned to a hero's welcome.
We accorded him a hero's welcome.
The story ends with the hero's death.
The President laid a wreath of flowers on the hero's grave.
The hero's predicament is foreshadowed in the first chapter.
The events of the hero's childhood are shown as a series of flashbacks.
He was given a hero's welcome when he returned home after winning the race.
Here's the latest wrinkle in the story  we find out that the villain is actually the hero's father!
